A sweeping aerial view of Singapore's Marina Bay skyline at twilight, rendered in Studio Ghibli animation style with soft watercolor textures and dreamy pastel clouds. In the foreground, a lone figure sits on a rooftop garden, gazing wistfully at a distant convention center glowing with warm golden light where silhouettes of people gather excitedly. The contrast between the solitary observer and the bustling event creates a mood of longing and isolation. Fireflies drift lazily through the humid tropical air, and lush green plants frame the scene. The iconic Singapore skyline features fantastical architectural details with curved organic shapes typical of Ghibli aesthetics, while paper lanterns float gently between buildings.
